\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

 out of the best 
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

 arms in an 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

-armed stochastic multi-armed bandit.
 Framed in the PAC setting, this particular problem generalises both the
 problem of 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

best subset selection
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


